# Cursor.ai Rules

**⚠️ DEPRECATED: See AGENTS.md instead**

This file is kept for historical reference. All guidance has been consolidated into **`AGENTS.md`** as the single source of truth for agents and developers.

---

## Quick Reference (See AGENTS.md for full details)

- **Package manager:** Bun 1.3.13 — use `bun run`, `bun install`, `bun exec`, `bunx`
- **Source of truth:** `AGENTS.md` (all architecture, patterns, conventions, testing, deployment)
- **Pre-PR checklist:** `bun run format && bun run type-check && bun run lint:strict && bun run verify:rules`
- **Environment:** Use `app-config.ts` (not `process.env` directly)
- **DB access:** DAL helpers only (not direct imports in UI)
- **Commits >7 files:** Require `.opencode/commands/*.plan.md` before committing
- **Provenance:** Include `Co-authored-by: Claude <copilot@opencode>` for AI-assisted changes

